{"title":"高帽儿（图片）","authors":["罗绍书","华君武"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"高帽儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗绍书诗  华君武画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卿卿来自远古，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今我兴味尤浓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时自作自戴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时承友加封。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或得意于小巷斗室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或忘形于大庭广众。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴了十顶百顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来不觉头痛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讥笑其奈我何？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒家自有妙用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕清风乍起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还我武大真容。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}